id, W. Allan (Derby)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Windsor-Clive, Lieut.-Colonel G.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Leech, Dr. J. W.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Rickards, G. W. (Skipton)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Winterton, Rt. Hon. Earl</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Lees-Jones, J.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Robinson, J. R. (Blackpool)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Wise, A. R.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Leighton, Major B. E. P.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Ropner, Colonel L.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Wolmer, Rt. Hon. Viscount</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Lennox-Boyd, A. T. L.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Ross, Major Sir R. D. (Londonderry)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Womersley, Sir W. J.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Levy, T.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Ross Taylor, W. (Woodbridge)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Wood, Hon. C. I. C.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Lewis, O</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Rowlands, G.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Wood, Rt. Hon. Sir Kingsley</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Liddall, W. S.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Royds, Admiral Sir P. M. R.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Wragg, H.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Lipson, D. L.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Ruggles-Brise, Colonel Sir E. A.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Wright, Wing-Commander J. A. C.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Little, Sir E. Graham.</td>